# TTCut-ng is a Linux-only project: enforce LF line endings for every
# text file, in the repository and in the working tree. Git auto-detects
# binary files via its NUL-byte heuristic and leaves them untouched; the
# explicit binary entries below are belt-and-braces for common formats.

* text=auto eol=lf

*.qm   binary
*.png  binary
*.jpg  binary
*.gif  binary
*.ico  binary
*.pdf  binary
